Name:Fletcher
Desc:In the first night, they must select a player who will become their customer. They may not select themselves. The Fletcher's customer gains the abilities of a huntress if they were to die. When the Fletcher wakes up in subsequent night, they may decide to permanently revoke the granted huntress abilities of the customer. The customer is not informed of gaining the abilities of a huntress, nor are they informed of the ability being revoked.
Card:In the first night, the Fletcher must select a player who will become their customer. Their customer gains the abilities of a huntress. When the Fletcher wakes up in subsequent night, they may decide to permanently revoke this power.
